18COMPONENT(ThreadTimeline) {
19 PROPS({
20 prof::context_t &ctx;
21 std::thread::id thd_id;
22 prof::time_point now;
23 double time_scale = 1.0;
24 int point_event_radius = 6;
25 })
26 INIT(ThreadTimeline) {
27
28 }
29
30 REDRAW {
31
32 add({
33 COMP(Canvas)({
34 .props = {
35 .draw = [this](vg::vg_fragment_t &frag) {
36 auto &thd_ctx = props.ctx.threads[props.thd_id];
37
38 // Paint timeline
39 frag.append(
40 vg::line {}
41 .stroke({.color = "#FCAE1E"_color})
42 .x1(0)
43 .y1(dim->ch.val() / 2)
44 .x2(dim->cw.val())
45 .y2(dim->ch.val() / 2)
46 );
47
48 // Paint events
49 int x = 0;
50 int w = 0;
51 for (const auto &ev: std::ranges::reverse_view(thd_ctx.timeline)) {
52 if (nullptr == ev.description || '\0' == *ev.description) continue;
53 x = dim->cw.val() - (int) ((double) prof::duration_cast<prof::microseconds>(
54 props.now - ev.t0).count() * props.time_scale);
55 if (ev.t1.has_value()) {
56 w = (int) (((double) prof::duration_cast<prof::microseconds>(
57 ev.t1.value() - ev.t0).count()) * props.time_scale);
58 if (x + w > 0) {
59 frag.append(
60 vg::rect {}
61 .x(x)
62 .y(0)
63 .width(int {std::max(w, 1)})
64 .height(dim->ch.val())
65 .fill({.color = "#FCAE1E"_color})
66 );
67 }
68 } else {
69 if (x + w > 0) {
70 frag.append(
71 vg::circle {}
72 .cx((x < 0 ? 0 : x) - props.point_event_radius)
73 .cy((dim->ch.val() / 2) - props.point_event_radius)
74 .r(int {props.point_event_radius})
75 .fill({.color = "#00CFCC"_color})
76 );
77 }
78 }
79 }
80 }
81 },
82 .w = dim->cw,
83 .h = dim->ch,
84 })
85 });
86 };
87};
